arity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowerment-campaign</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國人權基金會成立「香港專案小組」<span style=\"color: red;\">[尚欠19萬]</span> </strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=cf2542ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【登記選民，請即行動！】</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W7tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=ad077bae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位</div>"},{"pid":"e6b2d186463c1634de8a64e5198ec3bfc4680aea","tid":1968184,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:22:50.000Z","msg":"詳細就唔想多講。<br />\n<br />\n朋友前幾年開始年成日搵埋d 血腥、重口味、黑暗、恐怖、色情類既片睇。因為普通野已經滿足唔到佢。好奇心驅使下，開始越踩越深，走去研究連登。<br />\n<br />\n朋友年尾因為精神出現問題，而家仲睇緊心理輔導同精神科醫生。佢年尾出事，完全訓唔到、頭痛、好多野諗...佢同醫生講， d電影畫面恐怖影像入哂腦，合埋眼都已經有影像出現。感覺世界很可怕，越唔想去諗越會出現 ... 上過連登搵片都係佢細佬事後同我地講返。原來朋友圈子入面原全唔知佢走去掂呢味野，平時見面都冇提過。奉勸各位，得閒睇下甜片甜相好勒。我見到而家朋友個樣，我唔想越來越多人，因為好奇而攪到一去不返..."},{"pid":"bb83624470ad4a204e21cd26c9c9301dbbdc85a7","tid":1968184,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:23:18.000Z","msg":"上前線咪得"},{"pid":"f5d063855ad22eb89edca632324c81148bc12e4b","tid":1968184,"uid":222795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:24:40.000Z","msg":"驚又可以長年主動研究到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔小心睇到張皮肉分離相都拿拿聲滑過啦"},{"pid":"ac5a75e82e7beec5fbf49eb224a1fb8a6a2e7539","tid":1968184,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"又 loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal